<div class="mb-6">
  <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">내 관리자 계정의 비밀번호를 바꿉니다. 다른 운영자의 비밀번호는 여기서 바꿀 수 없습니다.</p>
</div>

<div class="max-w-lg">
  <% if (notice) { %>
    <div class="mb-4 rounded-md border border-green-200 bg-green-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-green-900">
      <i class="bi bi-check-circle mr-1"></i><%= notice %>
    </div>
  <% } %>
  <% if (error) { %>
    <div class="mb-4 rounded-md border border-red-200 bg-red-50 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-red-800">
      <i class="bi bi-exclamation-circle mr-1"></i><%= error %>
    </div>
  <% } %>

  <div class="bg-white shadow-sm rounded-xl p-6 border border-gray-100">
    <dl class="mb-5 pb-5 border-b border-gray-100 text-sm">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <dt class="text-gray-500">아이디</dt>
        <dd class="font-medium text-gray-800"><%= admin.username %></dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-2">
        <dt class="text-gray-500">등록 이메일</dt>
        <dd class="font-medium text-gray-800"><%= admin.email || '미등록' %></dd>
      </div>
    </dl>

    <form method="POST" action="/admin/account/password" class="space-y-4">
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5">현재 비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" name="current_password" required autocomplete="current-password"
               class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500">
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5">새 비밀번호</label>
        <input type="password" name="new_password" required minlength="8" autocomplete="new-password"
               class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500">
        <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-gray-400">8자 이상. 다른 곳에서 쓰지 않는 값으로 정하세요.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 mb-1.5">새 비밀번호 확인</label>
        <input type="password" name="confirm_password" required minlength="8" autocomplete="new-password"
               class="w-full px-3 py-2.5 rounded-lg border border-gray-200 text-sm focus:border-blue-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500">
      </div>
      <div class="pt-1">
        <button type="submit"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center h-[38px] px-5 text-sm font-medium rounded-md bg-blue-600 text-white hover:bg-blue-700">
          비밀번호 변경
        </button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>

  <p class="mt-4 text-xs text-gray-400">
    임시 비밀번호로 로그인했다면 지금 바로 바꿔 주세요. 임시 비밀번호는 메일에 그대로 남아 있습니다.
  </p>
</div>
